Machine Learning
 (41204) @ Chicago Booth


If you are visiting this site in Fall 2015, we predict with 
90% confidence that you're among the Booth students who, together with us, make some nice history. :)


This inaugural Machine Learning course specially tailored for MBAs is the 
very first of its kind in any curricula of the leading U.S. and international business schools
 that we know of.
